Hey Otto.

107
00:10:07.000 --> 00:10:08.400
Key.

108
00:10:10.960 --> 00:10:14.840
I should have listened to
you. Rinus. I didn't.

109
00:10:16.080 --> 00:10:17.680
I...

110
