Guys. what did I
say? Come here.

197
00:23:10.920 --> 00:23:13.440
Grab your bag. Rayan. Kaoutar too.

198
00:23:15.240 --> 00:23:18.120
Pack everything you need.
You too. come.

199
00:24:15.560 --> 00:24:18.280
Mr. Al Saddiqi. you need
to get out of here.

200
